arts.ttl: Fiorentina 3-4 Betis (AET): Ezzalzouli fires Betis to first European final
arts.sum: Abde Ezzalzouli smashed home minutes into extra time to send Real Betis into the Europa Conference League final at the expense of two-time finalists Fiorentina.
